price: 17. Ma mid (waa Alle'e) wax abuura baa la mid ah kuwo aan wax abuurin (sanamada)? Ma waydaan waansameyn?
arabic: أَفَمَن يَخۡلُقُ كَمَن لَّا يَخۡلُقُۚ أَفَلَا تَذَكَّرُونَ

version.title: Somali translation - Jacob
version.description: Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur'an into the Somali language, translated by Abdullah Hasan Jacob.
